President Cyril Ramaphosa says he is confident of investor pledges coming out of the fourth Investment Conference in Sandton. Courtesy #DStv403 JOHANNESBURG - President Cyril Ramaphosa says he is confident of investor pledges coming out of the fourth Investment Conference in Sandton. Critics are not so optimistic citing the ongoing energy crisis READ: Ramaphosa confident of investor pledges Ramaphosa opened the conference on Thursday morning.